### Hadith 2:324

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

Allah's Apostle said, "When anyone of you stands for the prayers, Satan
comes and puts him in doubts till he forgets how many Rakat he has
prayed. So if this happens to anyone of you, he should perform two
prostrations of Sahu while sitting.

